question: Siaⁿ-lí chòe-koâiⁿ ê ha̍p-chok-chiá sī siáng?
Tī só͘-chāi ê kok-chūng pí-sài tang-tiong, bat kiò-chòe 'runner-up' ê lóng-chóng sò͘-liōng ū kúi-ki?
Kiánn-siâu ê tē-khuài siat-chè (surface) téng-bīn, uī-liáu hō͘ i-ê tui-tú-chiá chòe-būi ê championship, sī siáng?
Chiu-kái siong-chhut chū siúⁿ-chi̍t-pái chhut-hiān kàu siūⁿ-chòe āu-chi̍t-pái hō͘-chāi ê Pháiⁿ-kok Open kim-chiàⁿ ê piáu-hiān têng-tō͘.
answer: Tī Pháiⁿ-kok Open kim-chiàⁿ tiong ê piáu-hiān sī chi̍t-ê chhián-lo̍h ê têng-tō͘. Siúⁿ-chi̍t-pái chhut-hiān tī 2003 nî tì-sū chi̍t-ê iâⁿ-kòe, tān-sī āu-lâi ê nn̄g-pái chhut-hiān tī 2006 nî kap 2007 nî lóng kiat-sòk chòe jī-miâ, chioh tāi-piáu tùi tōa tiâu-siâⁿ ê piáu-hiān chi̍t-ê lo̍h-hiat.

question: Tōa-sòe 2007 nî ê koàⁿ-chhiú-pái ê koàⁿ-chhiú-pái ê lia̍t-chhut?
Tī âng-chháu koân téng tńg bē, ū sì-phiah ê siúⁿ-koân sī tit-seng ê?
Nāi-suán siáng-chèⁿ hāi-sài ū sùⁿ sam-lú-sài ê sî, nāi-suán ê sùn-hóe lóng tò-chhe, chiū-sī tē-it-pái chòe-chòe-chòe ê sin chē-chē ê sùn-hóe ê chē-chē ê sò͘-ba̍t ū chē-chē?
Txuán-chú 'Virginia Ruano Pascual Paola Suárez' ê tūi-iâⁿ kah kiat-kó ū sán-seng sím-mih koan-hē? Kái-soeh chi̍t-ē.
answer: Ū, sī ū hó ê koan-hē. Tī nn̄g pái kah 'Virginia Ruano Pascual Paola Suárez' tūi-iâⁿ ê coin-chhiú chòe chūi-chhiú ê sî, kiat-kó lóng sī 'Winner'. Chit chióng sī tùi chit ê te̍k-tīm tūi-iâⁿ lâi kóng, chāi coin-chhiú ê sî, ū 100% ê sêng-kong lu̍t.

question: Koh-choán ê 'Championship' lia̍t ū piāu tī saⁿ lāi ê sò͘-jī, chiah-ê sò͘-jī tī chu-liāu lāi ū sím-mih ì-gī?
answer: ‘Championship’ lia̍t ū piāu tī saⁿ lāi ê sò͘-jī. Chiah-ê sò͘-jī, chhin-chhiūⁿ ‘Wimbledon (2)’ lāi-bīn ê ‘(2)’, sī piáu-sī chi̍t ê kiò-chiá tī chiah-ê chu-liāu-kù tiong, tùi chi̍t ê te̍k-tēng ê championship chham-sài ê sûn-sū lūi-sū, m̄-sī chha̍h-chha̍h ê thoân-chūi-sài pian-hō.

question: Koh chiat championship loh-suan sī ēng chē-chōa kó͘-chūi-á lâi-hōⁿ-chē, hām i ê piásu sī siáⁿ-chōa?
2001 nî Wimbledon coin-tó, sèng-chha̍h ê tùi-chhiú sī siáng?
